name: Green Ladybug Flower Clip w/ Red Headband
description:
This green flower clip is awesome on the headband it comes with.  BUT, that's not all it's good for.  WeCycle's intention is for this clip to be REUSED...in your hair, on a hat, on a bag, on a gift...get creative!  These are popular with little girls and big girls (yes you Mamas!) alike.

These clips make great gifts and are packaged and ready to go for re-sale.  Please ask me about wholesale pricing!

Each clip is handmade with love by WeCycle.  Young children should be supervised when wearing clips made by WeCycle as they may contain small parts that could present a choking hazard.

name: Lavender Marabou Feather Clip w/ Butterfly
description: This cute clip is made out of lavender marabou and is embellished with a butterfly.  Clip it in your hair, on a bracelet or on the bottom of your shirt for a look that really stands out.  Where else would you wear it??

name: Pink & Black Marabou Feather Puff Clip
description:
This spunky pink & black marabou puff is attached to a clip that can be clipped on to just about anything!  It goes great in your hair but is meant to be REUSED on your clothes, bags, belts, jewelry.  Why not throw one in your dog's hair?  They deserve to look BEAUTIFUL, too, right?

These clips come attractively packaged and make great gifts.  They are also packaged and ready for re-sale.  Ask me about wholesale pricing!

name: Deep Red Orchid Flower Clip
description:
This lovely clip makes an elegant statement.  Clip it in your hair, on your blouse or top off a flawlessly wrapped package with it.  Make sure the recipient knows to reuse it themselves!

These clips come packaged for re-sale, so please ask me about wholesale pricing.

name: Stretch Bracelet w/ Flower
description:
This black bracelet made of stretchy fabric has a cream colored flower that sits atop it quite gracefully.  A black and white embellishment in the center makes the perfect accent!  These bracelets are loved by young and old alike.

Young children should be supervised when wearing clips and accessories made by WeCycle, as they may contain small parts that could present a choking hazard.
